            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Elia(?) a blameless Christian lived 17 years, 2 months and 12 days ... 8 days before the kalends of February</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription uses a cut down rectangular piece of a large high imperial monumental Latin text. Brown marks on both sides of the stone derive from a wooden frame used previously to display the plaque.</p>
            </div>
